"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">拍摄</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">工作，晚上则躲在房间</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">继</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">续完成故事脚本，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">并</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">且通过匿名的方式</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">发</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">到</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">电影公司老板的邮箱</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">用</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">自己</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">大</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">胆的</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">构</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">思推动</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">真</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">实故事的发展，让罪犯一个个开始现形。</span></span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">此</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">时</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">的她除</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">去了</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">眼</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">镜，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">画上</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">了精致的妆容，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">变</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">得丰满、立体，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">同时又展现出过</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">人的</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">沉</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">稳与冷</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">静</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">。她与男友亚历桑德罗的关系</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">也开</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">始</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">悄</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">然</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">发生</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">变化。</span></span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">瓦</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">莱里亚每天</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">仍</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">然坚持</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">看</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">望</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">昏迷</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">中的男友，跟</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">他</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">说</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">说</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">自己的心</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">里</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">话，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">即使撞</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">见</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">亚</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">里桑德罗的另一个女友</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">时</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">也是</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">出乎意料地平静，甚至还推荐她进了剧</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">组</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">其</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">实</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">亚里桑德罗</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">背着她所</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">做的一切似乎她都心知肚明，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">从某种程度上来说，或许她</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">是</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">世间</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">最了解</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">亚里桑德罗</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">的人。</span></span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">无</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">论是</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">对</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">于这个花花公</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">子的生</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">命还是情感，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">瓦</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">莱里亚都</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">没</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">有放弃。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">她</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">的执着终于唤醒了亚历</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">桑</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">德罗</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">的</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">爱，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">让</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">这个</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">男</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">人明白瓦莱里亚对</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">他</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">是如此的重要。</span></span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">③&nbsp;女性的创造力</span></span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">女</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">性</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">身</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">体上的隐喻</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">本身就拥有了</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">创</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">造</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">力</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">女性</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">的</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">子宫</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">就是天然孕育与</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">创造新生命</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">的地方</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">。</span></span></span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">充</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">当幕后英雄的瓦莱里亚，在</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">白</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">发</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">老</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">人提供给</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">她故事</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">线索之后，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">开始了创作，这个令人惊艳的故事，引领她走向创作的巅峰。</span></span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">从</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">一开始，白发老人</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">与</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">瓦莱</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">里亚之间就似乎</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">有着不同寻</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">常</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">的关系</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">最后，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">从</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">母亲的口中，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">真的印</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">证了这个猜测。原来，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">白发老人原来是瓦莱里亚的</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">父亲</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">，是</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">一个专门与黑社会周旋</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">、有着强烈正义感</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">的大</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">侦探。母亲</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">在生下瓦莱里亚</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">之</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">后，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">为</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">了保护这个</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">孩子</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">，与父亲</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">断绝</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">了来往。</span></span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">父亲往</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">往是我们的理想化客体，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">是一股</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">牵引一个人</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">走</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">向成功</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">的力量。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">父</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">性</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">力量的介入，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">让她的</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">女性力量与男性力量得到了整合</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">，不仅女性魅力得到了彰显，创造力得到扩展</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">，还在被卷入错综复杂的案件中后，表现出了男性的冷静与沉着，最终与父亲联手，与黑手党斗智斗勇，阻止了名画的交易，同时亦让自己成功脱险。</span></span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">女性的成功与成熟，首先是通过向母亲的认同来完成自己向女性身份的认同，欣赏自己的女性魅力，获得创造力，然后通过父性力量的托举来获得理想与勇气，助力女性到达成功的彼岸。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> </div> </div>', '2022-01-12 19:12:11', '2022-03-17 18:35:00', '关于自我', '有很多孩童式的幻想，却无法在现实层面', '546');
INSERT INTO `ms_essay` VALUES (2, 2, '这一生我们都在寻找确定的爱《请回答1988》德善和阿泽', '<div class=\"cover-con\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; text-align: center;\"> <div class=\"cover-con\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #111111; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: #ffffff;\"></div> <div class=\"yxl-editor\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 0px; padding: 16px 0px 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; word-break: break-all; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; background-color: #ffffff;\"> <div class=\"yxl-editor-article \" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; min-height: 48px;\"> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">春节期间，再刷韩剧《请回答1988》，这部剧承载了七零，八零年代人满满儿时回忆，那些一起玩到大的小伙伴，一起串门看电视，上学，那些热心邻居叔叔阿姨们，那些我们逝去的美好的年少时光啊，都回来了。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <blockquote style=\"margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border-left-width: 4px; border-left-color: #999999; color: #999999;\"> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">《请回答1988》以五个小伙伴，德善、善宇、正焕、阿泽、娃娃鱼之间的友谊和爱情为主线，讲述1988年韩国汉城（现为首尔）奥运会历史背景下，双门洞弄堂里的五个家庭之间的温暖故事。</p> </blockquote> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 90%; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: block;\" src=\"https://ossimg.xinli001.com/20220223/fedbfa01617ba365cd645248560a80bc.jpeg?x-oss-process=image/quality,Q_80\" /></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">其中最让人牵挂的是德善和阿泽、正焕之间的爱。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">那个一天大呼小叫，一看书就睡觉，但却善良可爱的德善最后到底跟谁在一起了？</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">那个多年后和德善一起接受采访已经长残的家伙到底是谁啊？</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">阿泽，还是正焕？</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">而关于德善的爱恋走向证明了一件事，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">那就是我们终其一生，都在寻找一份确定的爱。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">01</span></h1> <h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">安全依恋关系</span></h1> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">从心理学上来说，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">人都有依附的需要。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">婴儿时期的我们无比脆弱，需要依靠父母才能活下去。这个时候，母亲主要为其提供的安全基地（主要养育者）。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">因此在早期的关系中，我们的依恋需要如果能得到及时满足，体验到爱和信任，孩子就会形成安全型的依恋关系，会觉得自己是可爱的，值得信赖的。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">反之如果孩子的依恋需要没有得到满足，安全型依恋没有养成，他可能对自己形成一个不好的印象，会觉得别人认为他不是可爱的，不值得被爱的。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">长大成人后，除了小时候形成的安全感，我们还会需要环境提供的安全感，而<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">伴侣就是我们成年之后的最重要的外在安全基础。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">《请回答1988》里，德善是家里的二女儿，她学习一般，性格大大咧咧，有一个学霸且脾气暴躁，一言不发就收拾人的姐姐宝拉。还有一个生来就备受宠爱的弟弟余晖，夹在中间的她常常是父母&ldquo;忽略&rdquo;的对象。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">德善每年跟着姐姐一起过生日，没有自己的生日蛋糕，尽管她抗议多次。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">将邻居送的烤鸡带回家，两只鸡腿分给了姐姐和弟弟，自己只分到一块鸡翅。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">这样的情况还有很多。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 90%; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: block;\" src=\"https://ossimg.xinli001.com/20220223/94b8766ef9b637b6881012c67685cd3d.jpeg?x-oss-process=image/quality,Q_80\" /></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">在她终于忍不住爆发后，爸爸为她单独买了小蛋糕并道歉：</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&ldquo;爸爸也是第一次当爸爸！&rdquo;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">就在德善和观众眼含泪花，以为她终于被看见的时候；</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">下一个镜头里，一家人蜂窝煤中毒，爸妈连喊带叫地拖出了宝拉和余晖，劫后余生般地躺在地上大口呼吸新鲜空气的时候，却发现，少了一个人，德善又被忘了。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">德善的成长的过程，其实是她不断寻求被多看见一点，被多重视，疼爱一点的过程。可以说孩童时代在这种被忽略的环境中长大，很难形成稳定的&ldquo;自我感&rdquo;。那么在未来的关系构建中，他们会倾向于从一下几方面，来试图稳定自我感：</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <blockquote style=\"margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border-left-width: 4px; border-left-color: #999999; color: #999999;\"> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">1.需要不断被赞善，感到被肯定。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">无论是在生活或情感中，不断寻求肯定，甚至可能为了肯定而掏空自己。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">2.需要从全面掌控和完全透明的关系状态中获得安心。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">在亲密关系中，他们需要全面掌控或完全透明的关系状态，才能让他们感觉被爱和安心。但这也常常让另一半窒息。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">3.从安稳的关系中，获得安全感。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">他们渴望从安稳的关系中，获得修复和替代性的安全感。</p> </blockquote> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">可以说，德善幼时形成的依恋模式，决定了她最终会和谁在一起。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <h1 class=\"pgc-h-center-line\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; text-align: center;\" spellcheck=\"false\" data-track=\"178\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">02</span></h1> <h1 class=\"pgc-h-center-line\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; text-align: center;\" spellcheck=\"false\" data-track=\"178\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">正焕和阿泽的爱</span></h1> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">阿泽和正焕，剧中最让人欲罢不能的两个男孩，</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">一个阳光温暖，一个默默守护；</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">而编导也貌似故意设定这样的情节，让我们不停去猜，到底是谁陪德善走到了最后？</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">1.正焕，让德善患得患失的爱</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">正焕，很早就喜欢德善了，只是他的爱一直像歌词&ldquo;爱你在心口难开&rdquo;一样，从不开口表白，只是用行动默默守护着德善。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">德善晚上去自习室，他会在窗前等着德善回来，才熄灯睡觉；</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">有时候德善实在太晚回家，他担心自己犯困睡过去了，还调好闹钟。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">为了跟德善一起上学，早早在德善门前守候，可德善一出门，他就假装刚到的样子蹲下系鞋带。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">在校车上为了保护她，用胳膊和身体在德善身旁围了一圈，手臂因为拥挤的人群和车子急刹青筋爆出。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">不但将爱意深埋内心，还成了&ldquo;口是心非&rdquo;的男孩，</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">在小伙伴问德善是否漂亮的时候，大声地说：&ldquo;当然是丑了！&rdquo;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">在德善的闺蜜问他是不是喜欢德善，坚定地说：不是。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">德善在朋友的鼓励下主动询问正焕心意时，他犹豫了半天最后捧起德善的脑瓜子说：</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&ldquo;用你这个脑袋好好想一想。&rdquo;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 90%; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: block;\" src=\"https://ossimg.xinli001.com/20220223/e6e3fa2f56caf117172a617532ce58a9.jpeg?x-oss-process=image/quality,Q_80\" /></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">即使到最后，就在他表白并送出戒指的时候，就在我们为他终于有勇气面对自己的爱而开心的时候，他却以&ldquo;开玩笑&rdquo;一带而过；</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">那个时候，好想冲上前给他一巴掌：</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">说出来又怎么样啊？笨蛋！至少你还有一个机会啊！</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">正焕对德善的爱，总是在等，等着德善总有一天发现。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">他的爱欲言又止，口是心非、反复无常总是让德善陷入怀疑的境地之中，他到底爱我吗？</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">2.阿泽，确定而又温暖的爱</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">阿泽，那个围棋天才少年，那个一笑可以融化世间所有不快的大男孩。他对德善的爱是确定而又温暖的。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 90%; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: block;\" src=\"https://ossimg.xinli001.com/20220223/0e22d3e09f441aa833cb0b0665d63e76.jpeg?x-oss-process=image/quality,Q_80\" /></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">从一开始所有人知道，他喜欢德善。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">当着小伙伴们面表白说：</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&ldquo;不是朋友，是作为女人，我喜欢她。&rdquo;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">连阿爸都知道他的喜欢方式：&ldquo;喜欢谁就拼命使唤谁。&rdquo;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">他喜欢德善的疯，</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">喜欢她嘴里包着饭大呼小叫的样子；</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">德善跳舞手脚不协调在他眼里都是可爱的；</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">德善涂了一个不一样的口红，只有他说：&ldquo;好看，比李英爱都还好看。&rdquo;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">他爱德善，只因为她是她。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <blockquote class=\"pgc-blockquote-abstract\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border-left-width: 4px; border-left-color: #999999; color: #999999;\"> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">发展心理学研究发现，在自我认知脆弱不稳定的成年早期，亲密同伴对我们的自我概念形成起着关键作用。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">如果身边有着能充分接纳我们的亲密伙伴，我们就能形成健康，积极的自我认知，觉得自己是好的、是有价值的。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">反之，我们可能会怀疑自身价值甚至自我贬低。</p> </blockquote> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">正焕对德善的&ldquo;打击和否定&rdquo;不一定是恶意，但他的话，很可能让本就自我感不稳定的德善更有挫败感。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">相比之下，阿泽对德善则是一种无条件的接纳，他爱着德善最真实的样子。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <h1 class=\"pgc-h-center-line\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; text-align: center;\" spellcheck=\"false\" data-track=\"103\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">03</span></h1> <h1 class=\"pgc-h-center-line\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; text-align: center;\" spellcheck=\"false\" data-track=\"103\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">确定的爱勇敢说出来</span></h1> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">《请回答1988》的高潮时刻，</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">当得知德善被约会对象抛弃一个人在剧院的时刻，正在看电影的正焕再也忍不住了，他夺门而出向德善的地方冲去，一路上红灯不断，我们跟他一起着急，也为他开心，这个内敛的男孩终于放下面子，放下拧巴，直面他和德善的爱。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">近了，近了，他的德善就在眼前，</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">那各穿着拖鞋在剧院门口被冻得瑟瑟发抖的德善回过头，吃惊地看着那个脚踩祥云从天而降的王子......</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">他来晚了一步，阿泽已经捷足先登了。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">他转身，泪流满面，机缘啊，总是差了那么一点；</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">他的德善真的离开他了。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">真的全怪机缘吗？就如他最后反省说的：</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <blockquote style=\"margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border-left-width: 4px; border-left-color: #999999; color: #999999;\"> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">但是缘分</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">还有时机</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">不是自动找上门的偶然</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">是带着恳切的盼望做出的无数选择</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">创造奇迹般的瞬间</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">毫不迟疑地放弃和当机立断</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">弄出了时机</p> </blockquote> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 90%; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: block;\" src=\"https://ossimg.xinli001.com/20220223/4e87e59b6b84b191e8343758f870f28d.jpeg?x-oss-process=image/quality,Q_80\" /></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">在阿泽这样确定的爱，爱她就勇敢表白面前，任何拧巴、犹豫、被动等待没有丝毫的招架之力。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">我们为正焕痛惜，那个刻骨铭心的女孩，那段欲言又止的初恋和他的青春也一块宣告结束。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">德善是幸福的，在她灿烂的青春岁月里，有那么两个男孩深深地爱着她。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">最终她收获了阿泽，一份确定而又温暖的爱。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">或许，我们每个人都希望能拥有这样一份确定的爱。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">从这个角度来说，我们每个人都能试着成为阿泽这样的恋人，给人以确定而又温暖的爱。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <h1 class=\"pgc-h-center-line\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; text-align: center;\" spellcheck=\"false\" data-track=\"217\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">04</span></h1> <h1 class=\"pgc-h-center-line\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; text-align: center;\" spellcheck=\"false\" data-track=\"217\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">给自己确定的爱</span></h1> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">但如果不能遇到，怎么办？</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">真正的一份确定的爱，有时可遇不可求，有的人终其一生也不可得。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">在我们这一生，原生家庭，伴侣，还有你自己是最重要的三个依靠。即使其它都不确定，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">但有一种爱是可以确定的，也无需去求，那就是对自己的爱。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">爱自己不需要任何条件，你不一定要非常优秀，不一定要完美，这丝毫不影响你爱自己，让你自己被爱滋养，在滋养中培养自己独立的自我和相对完整的人格。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">当你独立有自我，更有取悦自己的力量时，你可以更好地和他人相处，寻求更高质量的亲密关系。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">因为两性关系中，爱是彼此欣赏，彼此独立之上开出的美丽花朵。</p> </div> </div> </div>', '2022-01-12 19:14:17', '2022-03-17 18:35:05', '关于自我', '在我们这一生，原生家庭，伴侣，还有你自己是最重要的三个依靠。即使其它都不确定，但有一种爱是可以确定的，也无需去求，那就是对自己的爱。', '234');
INSERT INTO `ms_essay` VALUES (3, 3, '卫健委将心理教师配备比例与精神障碍管理，纳入考核', '<div class=\"cover-con\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; text-align: center;\"> <div class=\"cover-con\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #111111; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: #ffffff;\"> <div class=\"cover-con\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"></div> <div class=\"yxl-editor\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 0px; padding: 16px 0px 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; word-break: break-all; text-align: start;\"> <div class=\"yxl-editor-article \" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; min-height: 48px;\"> <h6 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400; color: #999999;\">文：喜猫</h6> <h6 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400; color: #999999;\">来源：微信公众号：心榜（ID：psytop）</h6> <h6 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400; color: #999999;\">原文标题：<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">定了！卫健委将心理教师配备比例与精神障碍管理，纳入健康中国行动年度考核</span></h6> <h6 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400; color: #999999;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></h6> <h6 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400; color: #999999;\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 90%; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: block;\" src=\"https://ossimg.xinli001.com/20220225/29cfc967bc986b96af4cfda8453dba66.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,Q_80\" /></h6> <h6 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400; color: #999999;\">&nbsp;</h6> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">你好，我是心理界乖巧的喜猫。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">今天，喜猫想跟大家分享一个消息：</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">本月16日的时候，卫健委官网发布了</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">《健康中国行动2021-2022年考核实施方案》</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">，在方案的考核指标体系中，明确将<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&ldquo;严重精神障碍患者规范管理率&rdquo;</span>与<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&ldquo;配备专职心理健康教育教师的中小学校比例&rdquo;</span>两项，纳入了考核中。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 90%; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: block;\" src=\"https://ossimg.xinli001.com/20220225/5741c5825e443331d792bcc506d261dd.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,Q_80\" /></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">《方案》明确，到2030年我国严重精神障碍患者规范管理率要达到<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">85%</span>，这一指标，超过国家卫健委2021年达到80%的要求。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">值得注意的是，文件同时要求，国家严重精神障碍信息系统登记在册的患者中，相邻两次随访间隔不超过3个月的患者数量。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">同时，《方案》也明确要求，到2030年，配备专职心理健康教育教师的中小学校比例要达到<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">90%</span>。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">这两个考核指标的纳入，意味着什么呢？</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">今天喜猫将从三个方面来跟大家探讨一下。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">01&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></h1> <h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">重要性</span></span></h1> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">《方案》的总体要求中，明确提到，设置考核的目的，是为了：</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <blockquote class=\"\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border-left-width: 4px; border-left-color: #999999; color: #999999;\" data-type=\"2\" data-url=\"\" data-author-name=\"\" data-content-utf8-length=\"114\" data-source-title=\"\">......强化省级党委和政府全面推进健康中国建设主体责任，推动各地健全完善组织推进机制，加大健康中国行动实施力度，加快把健康融入所有政策，形成&ldquo;大卫生、大健康&rdquo;工作格局，确保健康中国行动各项任务有效落实、主要目标指标如期实现。</blockquote> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">从这个信息中，我们可以看到的是，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">主体责任的明确</span>。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">喜猫之前，多次在文章中提到，政策虽好，重在落实。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">本次考核方案，明确了&ldquo;省级党委和政府&rdquo;作为推进健康中国建设的主体负责方，并且提出了明确的考核指标，要求确保&ldquo;各项任务有效落实、主要目标指标如期实现&rdquo;，在<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">促进政策的落地执行方面，起到了巨大的作用</span>。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">其次，则是要求中也提到要&ldquo;把健康融入所有政策&rdquo;，则意味着日后将有更多的政策倾向于健康建设，心理健康也会囊括其中。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">另外一个值得注意的是，虽然本次考核的目标值年限是2030年，但也提到&ldquo;考核工作原则上以年度为周期，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">每年开展一次考核</span>。&rdquo;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">这就意味着严重精神障碍患者规范管理和专职心理健康教育教师的中小学校配比虽然有一个长期目标，但每一年都需要进行考核，必须交出成绩。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">这也意味着政策执行过程中推诿、拖延的情况有可能因此得到改善。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">从总体上来说，将这两项指标纳入到健康中国行动的考核中，也意味着精神障碍的管理和中小学心理健康教育已经得到了国家的高度重视，将长期作为一个&ldquo;国策&rdquo;执行下去。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">不论是对精神障碍患者、校园儿童青少年，还是心理健康从业者来说，这都是一个好消息。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">02&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></h1> <h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">必要性</span></span></h1> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">每一个政策的出台，都不可能是空穴来风，而是有其必要性。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">这次将严重精神障碍管理，和学校心理教师配比纳入考核，也有其迫切的必要性。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">首先说说严重精神障碍管理。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">据《中国经济周刊》报道：中国确诊的重性精神障碍患者达1600万，但精神病院床位和执业医师的数量与之的比值却只有<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">1：121</span>和<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">1：842</span>。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">据卫生部调查，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">精神疾患在我国疾病总负担排名中居首位</span>，已超过心脑血管、呼吸系统及恶性肿瘤等疾患。各类精神问题约占疾病总负担的1/5。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">从数据上看，严重精神障碍患者往往是社会弱势群体。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">而绝大部分严重精神障碍的治疗，动辄就要数万乃至数十万。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">面对巨大的经济压力，许多病人家属不愿承担高额诊疗费用，拒绝将已基本康复的患者接出医院，有病人住院甚至超30年。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">这一情况，在农村，就更加严重。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">喜猫之前转过的《从丰县事件谈农村精神卫生：歧视严重，资源匮乏，锁在精神障碍患者身上的无形锁链该如何解开？》一文中，就提到：<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">中国整体的精神卫生资源本来就是不够的，只是在农村，许多问题更加突出。</span></span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">许多得不到社会支持，又没有足够的精神卫生资源保障的农村家庭，只能选择将患者锁在家中。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">这些情况，无疑会造成巨大的社会隐患。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">所以，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">严重精神障碍患者管理一直被列为心理体系建设的重点任务</span>，国家每年上半年会发布相关文件并公布具体指标，其重要性不言而喻。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">纳入考核，也是建设健康中国的必要之举。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">其次，将心理教师的配比率纳入考核，与近些年越来越严重儿童青少年心理问题相关。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">翻看这几年的新闻，学生跳楼，儿童青少年自残、自杀等各类新闻的比重，在逐步上升。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">去年，英国儿科领域权威SCI期刊Journal of Child Psychology and Psychiatry and Allied Disciplines（JCPP）在5月份发表了中国第一个全国性的儿童青少年精神障碍流行病学调查。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">调查显示，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">我国儿童青少年精神健康面临严峻挑战</span>，整体精神障碍流行率为17.5%。注意缺陷多动障碍、对立违抗障碍和重性抑郁障碍是儿童青少年中流行率最高的精神障碍。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">去年的一系列研究数据也显示出儿童心理健康面临重大挑战：</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <blockquote class=\"\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border-left-width: 4px; border-left-color: #999999; color: #999999;\" data-type=\"2\" data-url=\"\" data-author-name=\"\" data-content-utf8-length=\"215\" data-source-title=\"\"> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">国民心理健康调查（2021）显示：24.6%青少年抑郁筛出率。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">国家卫健委（2021）调查显示：17.5%青少年心理障碍的时点患病率。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">南京脑科医院（2021）调查显示：全球儿童青少年的非自杀性自伤的发生率约为19.5%，中国中学生群体的发生率为27.4%，非自杀性自伤行为在我国精神科就诊的患者中总发生率为6.8%（门诊）和6.5%（病房）。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">其中13~17岁发生率最高（15.9%），18~22岁其次（13.6%），其他年龄段较少。</span></p> </blockquote> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">在这种背景下，搭建校园心理健康体系，减少儿童青少年的心理问题，就成了全社会的焦点。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">其中，加强心理健康教育，引入更多的心理健康教师，对儿童青少年进行心理辅导与疏导，是一个关键环节。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">但我们要注意到的是，本次纳入考核的，仅仅是配备教师的学校数量比例。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">而这，还远远不够。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">03&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></h1> <h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">可能性</span></span></h1> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">虽然本次的方案，列出了两个明确的指标，但在喜猫看来，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">这两个指标还远不能有效地解决上述的必要性问题。</span></span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">但我们也可以从中看到一些可能性。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">就如上文所说，中国确诊的重性精神障碍患者达1600万，但精神病院床位和执业医师的数量与之的比值却只有1：121和1：842。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">而且据了解，我国精神卫生的财政投入也相对缺乏。2020年，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">精神卫生支出占全部卫生支出的比例不到2%。</span></span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">面对悬殊巨大的医患比例和杯水车薪的精神卫生资源，仅仅是加强&ldquo;规范管理&rdquo;是远不能解决当前的严重问题的。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">如何<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">加强精神卫生人才的建设与输出，提高精神卫生支出的财政比例</span>，才是问题的关键。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">值得注意的是，本次的考核中，也对&ldquo;每千常住人口执业（助理）医师数（人）&rdquo;和&ldquo;城乡居民医保政策范围内住院费用基金支付比例（%）&rdquo;提出了指标考核，要求2025年目标值达到3.2和70%。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">那么，接下来，是否可能出现更具体的政策，对精神卫生的&ldquo;执业（助理）医师数（人）&rdquo;提出要求，为精神疾病的&ldquo;住院费用基金支付比例&rdquo;划定目标，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">在&ldquo;规范管理&rdquo;的目标基础上，迈向&ldquo;有效治理&rdquo;</span>，也是值得我们期待的。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">其次，则是<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">心理健康教师的重要性，不仅是数量上的，更重要的是质量上的</span>。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">心榜的后台不时就能收到一些学校心理教师的留言，多数留言都提到学校心理教师的处境太过艰难：</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">因为不跟高考成绩挂钩，学校领导不重视心理教育，导致工作展开不顺利；</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">待遇偏低，不得不身兼多职，代理其他课程，压力过大；</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">行政工作过多，占据了大部分时间；</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">做咨询工作时被要求以学业为重，把心理咨询变成劝学；</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">学校不重视心理健康技能，缺乏培训安排；</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">评职称永远轮不上......</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">等等一系列问题，导致心理健康教师在学校里处境艰难，难以展开工作，甚至沦为摆设，只是为了应付上级检查而勉强设立。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">从这些情况来看，本次考核仅将配备教师的学校比例纳入考核，还远远不够，只是校园心理健康体系建设这趟千里之行迈出的第一步。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">在数量要求的基础上，是否可能出现更多的政策，对心理教师的工作加以支持，提高心理教师待遇，加重心理健康教育在课程中的比重，也是每一个有意进入学校工作的从业者值得关注和期待的动向。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">无论如何，这次《方案》的提出，对心理健康行业和从业者来说，总是释放出了一个利好的信号，也让我们看到了更多发展的可能性。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">我是喜猫，关注我，第一时间掌握心理行业资讯。</span></p> </div> </div> </div> </div>', '2022-01-12 19:15:35', '2022-03-17 18:35:10', '教育', '本月16日的时候，卫健委官网发布了《健康中国行动2021-2022年考核实施方案》，在方案的考核指标体系中，明确将“严重精神障碍患者规范管理率”与“配备专职心理健康教育教师的中小学校比例”两项，纳入了考核。', '46');
INSERT INTO `ms_essay` VALUES (4, 2, '辅导孩子写作业，你不必鸡飞狗跳', '<div class=\"cover-con\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; text-align: center;\"> <div class=\"cover-con\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #111111; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: #ffffff;\"> <div class=\"cover-con\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"> <div class=\"cover-con\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"></div> <div class=\"yxl-editor\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 0px; padding: 16px 0px 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; word-break: break-all; text-align: start;\"> <div class=\"yxl-editor-article \" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; min-height: 48px;\"> <h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: 16px;\" data-md5=\"91f70\">01</span></h1> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">随着双减政策的到来，家长们开始自己辅导孩子的作业。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">然而在辅导孩子写作业的过程中，很多家长是抓狂的。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">有父母说，我孩子总是拖拉，晚上写完作业都是半夜了，又要催促他快点睡觉，睡眠时间严重不够，影响他第二天在学校的学习状态。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">还有父母说，孩子坐不住，注意力不集中，一会这样一会那样，恨不得把他绑在板凳上写作业。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">甚至有父母会说，我情愿去吃工作的苦，也不吃辅导孩子写作业的苦，这样下去我和孩子倒不像是亲人，会变成仇人的啊。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">如果辅导孩子让亲子关系变了味，那么不妨停下脚步，思索一番：</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">在这个过程中，究竟是孩子的作业还是父母的作业？</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">究竟是孩子需要帮助还是父母满足了自己的无所不能？</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">究竟是孩子这个人重要还是孩子的作业重要？</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">如果你的出发点是帮助孩子，那么你得停下和孩子有关于作业的战争，进一步寻找到你们可以合作的方式。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">如果你的出发点是相信孩子，那么有时你得需要和孩子的作业之间保持一点距离，除非他真正的需要你的帮助。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">美国儿童心理学家德雷克斯说，忧虑的父母不信任自己，不信任孩子，也不信任将来，他们只能想到防守和预防。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">放下你的忧虑，学会信任孩子，是你们能够在孩子的作业上可以达成合作的前提。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">记得心理学者贺岭峰在谈到他女儿的教育时说，他知道女儿的数学很差，经常考不及格。有些题反复错，错了好几遍。他还被老师叫到学校，被老师批评。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">他说，如果女儿的数学老师都没法给她讲明白，我一个心理老师更是没办法讲明白了。即使这样，他也不亲自给女儿辅导作业，而是和女儿建立了一种自然亲密值得信任的关系，她女儿也在他的保护下走上了一条快乐学习的路。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">孩子学习的过程可以是快乐的，即使有很多困难和痛苦，也不应该是父母施加的，而是在学习知识、解决问题、能力成长的过程中自然存在的，相信每个孩子都有向上成长的力量，他们会找到一种甚至多种方法去一一面对和解决。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">所以，作为父母，我们在孩子的学习过程中，只能是配角，是孩子需要帮助时的帮助者和协助者，是有分寸和界限的陪伴者以及情感上的支持者，不可越俎代庖，不可替代孩子去学习。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /></span></p> <h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\" data-md5=\"91f70\">02</span></span></h1> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">关注孩子学习的时间安排。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">有一个孩子，常常写作业到晚上10点，效率特别低，经常写错别字，计算也出现很大的问题。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">仔细观察他学习的状态，他一会起喝水，走一圈回来又坐下写几个字。写了10分钟不到，他又去上厕所，一圈回来又写几个字。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">写了一会，又想起要喝点牛奶，于是反反复复的，他学习的注意力都被一些细枝末节的小事不断中断，看起来写了很久的作业，但其实是把时间完全浪费在和作业无关的事上，导致学习效率低下。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">当一个孩子无法静下来学习，注意力被严重破坏的时候，他的学习是混乱无序的。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">他不会合理安排学习时间。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">他甚至不知道自己需要花费多少时间才能完成作业。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">这样的孩子，会让很多家长头疼。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">家长急得骂孩子甚至动手，这不但没有效果，也会进一步让孩子有巨大的挫败感。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">没有孩子不爱学习，重要的是我们需要帮助他们建立一种高效学习的习惯。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">这需要从时间管理上开始。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">帮助孩子做时间计划是非常重要的一步，也就是一个孩子对于他自己的作业和学习要非常清楚。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">老师在课堂上布置了什么作业，需要一用本子记录下来，一条条的罗列出来。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">回到家，你可以问问孩子，今天老师布置作业的情况，然后帮助他回溯今天要做的事。他的计划是什么。学习时长是多久。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">是先做数学还是先做语文，数学花多长时间，语文花多长时间。在做作业之前，需要做什么准备工作。准备花多少时间。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">比如，是否需要吃点东西，喝水，上厕所。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">写作业的文具准备好了吗。铅笔、钢笔、直尺、三角板等等。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">写作业的书桌上是否保持整洁，没有其他干扰因素。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">做作业的过程中需要用到的工具书是否准备到位。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">时间管理中伴随着习惯的培养，当一个孩子知道每天需要做哪些事，长期如此会形成良好的习惯，而这些习惯有助于高效的完成作业。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\" data-md5=\"91f70\">03</span></span></h1> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">关注孩子遇到问题的态度。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">无论一个孩子多么优秀，在学习的过程中，一定会遇到难题无法解决。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">这时候，你关注孩子的状态，陪伴在他的左右，在他需要帮助时提供有效的帮助，这是孩子迫切需要的。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">但帮助孩子的过程中，主体是孩子，一定不是父母。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">举个例子：</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">有父母的学习成绩特别好，每次孩子遇到难题的时候，他都很乐意的刷刷的就帮助孩子做好了，可是孩子并不懂这道题是如何解决的。孩子还需要他再详细讲清楚的时候，他就不耐烦的开始责骂孩子怎么这么笨，这么简单的题都做不了之类。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">孩子只能默默承受这种打击。一方面他确实做不了，以后还要父母的帮忙，另一方面，他没有空间再往前去挑战，因为这样的父母就是一座巍峨的高山，他无法翻越。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">久而久之，留下的更可能是一个充满巨大自卑感的孩子。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">再比如说，一个孩子一遇到稍微困难的作业，不会多动一点脑筋，直接放弃，或者让父母帮自己做。这样的孩子，也就失去了学习的动力。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">这可能是在他学习的过程中，每遇到困难，总会有爸爸妈妈解决，做作业就变成了父母的事，和他没有什么关系。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">父母把孩子的作业变成了自己的作业。害怕孩子做不完作业，被老师批评，给自己丢脸，被同学嘲笑，等等原因，所以宁愿帮助孩子写作业，也不愿意孩子就此面对。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">久而久之，孩子一定会失去学习的动力。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">写作业从来不是父母的功能，帮助孩子有学习能力才是父母的功能啊。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">所以，当父母抱怨说，这个孩子就是不爱动脑筋的时候，需要反思一下，是不是你剥夺了孩子动脑筋的过程，全程代劳了孩子的学习。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">我们关注孩子遇到问题的态度，也才能选择合适的方法去帮助孩子。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">如果一个孩子遇到问题，会不停的请教或者查找资料，努力去寻找解决问题的方法，那么这个孩子是有学习的动力以及钻研精神的，这时，父母不要轻易出手，除非他已经用尽了所有的办法，开始向你求助。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">但如果一个孩子已经把做作业这件事当做了父母的事，需要你为他负责的时候，这时就需要警惕了：我们是不是做得太多？</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">退出孩子的学习世界，放下对孩子的学习控制，克制住想要帮他完成作业的心情，才能让他学会为自己的学习承担责任，让他找回学习的乐趣和动力。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\" data-md5=\"91f70\">04</span></span></h1> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\" data-md5=\"91f70\">&nbsp;</span></span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">关注孩子学习的感受。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">美国的儿童心理专家沙法丽&middot;萨巴瑞说，我们的关注点不再是孩子考试是否答对了全部的题目，而是他们做错了题目时的感受。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">学习的过程，有快乐也有痛苦，可能是自己努力之后全部做对的一种成就感和自豪感，也可能是做错题目之后的挫败感。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">一个孩子考100分固然值得父母骄傲，开心一整天，但如若做错题之后，就会被惩罚、责骂、打击，或者没有父母的好脸色，那么对于孩子来说，无疑只能是雪上加霜。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">孩子一定会把成绩和自我价值联系起来。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">也就是说，只有我考100分才是值得妈妈爱的，没考到<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">100</span>分就可能失去妈妈的爱。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">父母对待孩子分数的态度，也就是对待孩子做得不那么完美，甚至有一些学习困难的态度，会影响孩子如何看待学习，如何看待他在家庭中的位置，是否有价值感，是否被肯定，是否被接纳。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">所谓关注孩子学习的感受，是可以及时的分享孩子学习的喜悦成果，也可以及时安抚孩子考砸之后的落魄心情。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">比如：</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <blockquote style=\"margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border-left-width: 4px; border-left-color: #999999; color: #999999;\"> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: inherit;\">儿子：妈妈，我今天考试考了70分。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: inherit;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: inherit;\">妈妈：啊，有点意外呢。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: inherit;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: inherit;\">儿子：是的，我考了历史最低分，以前从来没有考过这么低的分。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: inherit;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: inherit;\">妈妈：恩，是的，是有点低，妈妈为你感到有一点遗憾，是你在学习的时候出了什么特别的状况吗？</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: inherit;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: inherit;\">儿子：也不是，就是做题的时候时间有点匆忙，我好几个题都看错了。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: inherit;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: inherit;\">妈妈：这样啊，那是有点可惜，后面需要妈妈帮助你在时间上做一些训练吗？</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: inherit;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: inherit;\">儿子：可以啊，我觉得我后面不可能考这么低了。</span></p> </blockquote> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: inherit;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">简单的和孩子谈谈他考砸时的心情，你也许会看到他，自己已经开始分析原因，并找到解决方法了。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">分数不是最重要的，它只是检测孩子学习结果的一种工具，最重要的是在这个过程中，孩子可以自己找到调整的方法，无论是学习方法和习惯的调整，还是情绪调整，都是孩子未来走向社会，适应社会，去创造生活的重要技能。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">而，作为父母，我们唯一能做的，就是保持对孩子的关注，给他理解和支持，并在他需要时赋予及时的帮助。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">最重要的是做孩子学习的&ldquo;心灵陪伴者&rdquo;，创造值得信任的亲子关系，你孩子的学习自然不会让你鸡飞狗跳。</span></p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div>', '2022-01-12 19:17:10', '2022-03-17 18:35:17', '关于自我', '作为父母，我们唯一能做的，就是保持对孩子的关注，给他理解和支持，并在他需要时赋予及时的帮助。最重要的是做孩子学习的“心灵陪伴者”，创造值得信任的亲子关系。', '23');
INSERT INTO `ms_essay` VALUES (5, 1, '《花园派对》：隐喻的背后，是对人类贪念的抨击', '<div class=\"cover-con\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; text-align: center;\"> <div class=\"cover-con\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #111111; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: #ffffff;\"> <div class=\"cover-con\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"> <div class=\"cover-con\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"> <div class=\"cover-con\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><img class=\"article-cover\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" title=\"《花园派对》：隐喻的背后，是对人类贪念的抨击-心理学文章-壹心理\" src=\"https://ossimg.xinli001.com/20220224/a44d7f81be616b2034d21a7b38a9c1d3.jpeg?x-oss-process=image/quality,Q_80\" alt=\"《花园派对》：隐喻的背后，是对人类贪念的抨击-心理学文章-壹心理\" /></div> <div class=\"yxl-editor\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 0px; padding: 16px 0px 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; word-break: break-all;\"> <div class=\"yxl-editor-article \" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; min-height: 48px;\"> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">美国著名人际关系学大师戴尔&bull;卡耐基曾说：&ldquo;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important;\">人的一生中会遇到很多陷阱，而在这些陷阱之中，最可怕的一种是自掘的陷阱，即贪婪。</span>因为贪心，人们会忽略自己的弱点，不顾一切地去满足自己的欲望。这时，即使危险摆在面前，也不理会、不避让，因为贪心遮住了眼睛，以致无法看到危险所在。&rdquo;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">是的，贪婪，让很多人陷入自己挖掘的陷阱中，无法自拔。就像贪吃者，让身体失去健康；贪权者，让自己失去自由；贪财者，让自己成为金钱的奴隶，等等。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><img class=\"syl-page-img\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 90%; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: block; height: auto;\" src=\"https://p26.toutiaoimg.com/origin/pgc-image/2c73823c8705471399b76ea65389b726?from=pc\" alt=\"动画短片电影《花园派对》：隐喻的背后，是对人类贪念的抨击\" data-local=\"false\" /></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">一部来自法国大学生创作的动画短片电影《花园派对》，从动物的视角出发，采用隐喻的方式，也给我们揭示了人性的贪婪。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <blockquote class=\"pgc-blockquote-abstract\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border-left-width: 4px; border-left-color: #999999; color: #999999;\"> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">这部电影时长不到八分钟，主要讲述的是看似人烟罕至的野外，随着镜头推移，发现这竟是一栋疏于打理的豪宅别墅。游泳池的水浑浊不堪，布满了落叶和绿藻。青蛙在水中自在游弋，引来岸上丑陋肥胖的蟾蜍的注意。不远处的树枝上，一只美丽的蝴蝶轻盈落下，近处的青蛙则盯上这华美的佳人，它步步紧逼，全然不顾周遭四伏的危险。装潢考究的卧室，衣物用品凌乱不堪，仿佛经历过一场又一场的纵欲狂欢。餐厅中央杯盘狼藉，蚊蝇飞舞，而那种肥硕的蟾蜍大快朵颐，饕餮无度。</p> </blockquote> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">影片中的主角是青蛙和蟾蜍，呈现的画面仿佛是不经意间扫过房屋每一个角落，包括毁坏的监视器，门窗上的弹孔，消失的主人，以及安静得让人可怕的氛围，暗示了这是一场血之盛宴。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">这部短片从剧情创作、精妙配乐、以及画面质感等方面都非常出色，获得第90届奥斯卡金像奖提名动画短片。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">今天的文章，我想从影片的隐喻来说说人性的贪婪，以及生活的真相。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><img class=\"syl-page-img\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 90%; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: block; height: auto;\" src=\"https://p26.toutiaoimg.com/origin/pgc-image/b049fe6d7d62419bab4626f9b12c4c7a?from=pc\" alt=\"动画短片电影《花园派对》：隐喻的背后，是对人类贪念的抨击\" data-local=\"false\" /></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <h1 class=\"pgc-h-arrow-right\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">01</span></h1> <h1 class=\"pgc-h-arrow-right\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">无法满足的性欲和食欲，</span></h1> <h1 class=\"pgc-h-arrow-right\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">展现的是人类的贪婪</span></h1> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">影片开头，一只青蛙跳入泳池，岸上的一只蟾蜍看见了，向其示好，但青蛙没理那只蟾蜍，走进了卧室，蟾蜍紧随其后。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">接着，镜头里出现另一只青蛙，在树上寻觅着&ldquo;对象&rdquo;，刚好一只蝴蝶出现，便奋不顾身扑过去，结果蝴蝶飞走，它差点儿从树上掉下来。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">再往下看，一只肥大的蟾蜍慢慢醒来，全然不顾苍蝇满天飞，大口大口吞下鱼子酱，结果因为贪吃瓶中的马卡龙，被困在瓶子里，直到重重地摔在地上才得以脱身。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><img class=\"syl-page-img\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 90%; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: block; height: auto;\" src=\"https://p26.toutiaoimg.com/origin/pgc-image/f3fc83434731448d93350696c96156bc?from=pc\" alt=\"动画短片电影《花园派对》：隐喻的背后，是对人类贪念的抨击\" data-local=\"false\" /></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">通过青蛙的择偶过程，以及蟾蜍的暴饮暴食，我们可以看到人类的身影。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">有些人的色欲永远无法满足，一直处于寻找另一半的过程中，而这样的人终究无法找到真爱，也享受不到爱情的温暖；有些人喜欢暴饮暴食，完全不考虑自己的身体状况，最后失去了健康。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">而影片中凌乱的床单，以及周围的装饰，也可以判断出这座别墅的主人就是纵欲之人；加上最后浮出水面的肥胖身躯，也可以断定必是暴饮暴食者。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">我们常说，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">过犹不及，一旦过了那个&ldquo;度&rdquo;就变成了贪婪</span>。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">这提醒我们在追求食欲和性欲时，一定要根据现实做出选择，这个现实包括身体的承受力，以及准确地认识自己。比如在追求爱情时，要先看清自己的现实，不要向影片中那只追求蝴蝶的青蛙，盲目乐观。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">当然，认清自己，是不容易的，但正因为不容易，才更值得去做。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><img class=\"syl-page-img\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 90%; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: block; height: auto;\" src=\"https://p26.toutiaoimg.com/origin/pgc-image/0d00da97e0bd47ef9f3c0b2de93698db?from=pc\" alt=\"动画短片电影《花园派对》：隐喻的背后，是对人类贪念的抨击\" data-local=\"false\" /></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <h1 class=\"pgc-h-arrow-right\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">02</span></h1> <h1 class=\"pgc-h-arrow-right\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">蛙与人的交互，</span></h1> <h1 class=\"pgc-h-arrow-right\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">亦是人与人的联结</span></h1> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">影片中那只追求蝴蝶的青蛙，追到了泳池的操作间，在蹦跳之间意外打开了开关，瞬间，原本死气沉沉的豪宅，变成青蛙和蟾蜍欢乐的海洋。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">随着一只只青蛙和蟾蜍不断涌现，它们在泳池中欢快游弋的景致，我们可以想象出当时豪宅里的场景&mdash;人与人之间谈笑风生，推杯换盏，不亦乐乎。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">但是，影片后面，我们看到青蛙和蟾蜍跳上浮出的尸体，不禁感慨世事无常。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">更重要的是，青蛙和蟾蜍们依然享受着这场花园派对，根本没有为失去生命的人类感到悲伤。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><img class=\"syl-page-img\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 90%; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: block; height: auto;\" src=\"https://p26.toutiaoimg.com/origin/pgc-image/e622247b8a9a4e4e86421eabe8682a75?from=pc\" alt=\"动画短片电影《花园派对》：隐喻的背后，是对人类贪念的抨击\" data-local=\"false\" /></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">其实，不仅仅因为它们是动物，即使是人类，人与人之间的真感情也很少。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">从尸体的腐烂程度、别墅的沉寂，以及到处凌乱的场景，就可以推测出，这位别墅的主人没有什么真正的朋友，当时一起纵情的朋友，估计早已离去。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">而这提醒我们，要把时间用在值得的人身上。花时间去经营真正的友情。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">虽然现在的联络方式方便快捷，但当自己遇到难处时，发现能够拨通电话的人少之又少，这说明自己的时间都浪费了。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">那么，什么才是真正的朋友呢？</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">真正的朋友，不会只考虑自己的得失，而是会考虑对方的利益，且把对方放在重要的位置上，更重要的是，真正的朋友，是值得信任的人。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><img class=\"syl-page-img\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 90%; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: block; height: auto;\" src=\"https://p26.toutiaoimg.com/origin/pgc-image/8fd17440e4b947b9b685c0c65b8b3f6b?from=pc\" alt=\"动画短片电影《花园派对》：隐喻的背后，是对人类贪念的抨击\" data-local=\"false\" /></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <h1 class=\"pgc-h-arrow-right\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">03</span></h1> <h1 class=\"pgc-h-arrow-right\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">真真假假的背后，</span></h1> <h1 class=\"pgc-h-arrow-right\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">即是生活真相的映射</span></h1> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">不得不说，这部影片的动画制作效果非常厉害，达到以假乱真的惊艳效果，而这也是生活的真相，即很多时候没有所谓的真相。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">换句话说，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">无常，便是真相。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">从影片中被洗劫一空的保险柜、摆在桌子上的手机、被破坏了的摄像头，以及泳池中浮出的一具男性尸体，我们可以脑补很多画面，不仅给观众留下很大的遐想空间，还说明了还原真相的困难重重。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">那位别墅的主人，本来享受着生活的美好，结果，那一切化为乌有，而平时无法靠近别墅的青蛙和蟾蜍，这时成为了主角。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">人类世界的疯狂过后，蛙蛙世界开启了狂欢之旅。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><img class=\"syl-page-img\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 90%; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: block; height: auto;\" src=\"https://p26.toutiaoimg.com/origin/pgc-image/a8742e0e0ae34c558b1d58f5338d728e?from=pc\" alt=\"动画短片电影《花园派对》：隐喻的背后，是对人类贪念的抨击\" data-local=\"false\" /></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">其实，这里还有一层隐喻，即人类与大自然的关系。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">那么，在我们懂得无常，不确定性是生活的真相后，该怎样活着呢？</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">首先，认清生活的真相后，依然热爱生活。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">也就是说，我们要在不确定性的生活状态中，找寻生命的意义，不要贪婪，懂得节制，尊重事实。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">其次，活在当下，把时间用在值得的地方。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">也就是说，我们无法拥有过去和未来，只能把握好现在， 把&ldquo;现在&rdquo;用在值得的地方，包括做好工作、经营好友情、爱情，以及亲情等等。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">再次，关注内聚性自我的形成，让自己更强大，更成熟。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">内聚性自我，是美国自体心理学创始人科胡特提出的一个概念。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">他认为，内聚性自我的形成，是心灵发展历程中的一个里程碑，也是情绪承受能力的关键，因为情绪的惊涛骇浪，只会让内聚性自我晃动，但不会轻易导致自我的瓦解。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <blockquote style=\"margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border-left-width: 4px; border-left-color: #999999; color: #999999;\"> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">内聚性自我中，有一种向心力，一个人的心灵碎片，都可以被凝聚在一起。这时的自己，就不会贪婪吃喝玩乐，因为那种无节制的生活方式，更多的是内心空虚；也不会那么在意所谓的朋友多少，因为那时的自己会尊重内心的选择，做对自己真正有意义的事情。</p> </blockquote> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">总之，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">这场花园派对，让我们看到了人类的贪婪、人与人之间的亲疏，以及生活的无常真相，而我们要做的就是过好现在的生活，节制有度，把时间花在值得的人和事上，并不断强大自我。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div>', '2022-01-12 19:19:36', '2022-03-17 18:35:24', '情绪', '“人的一生中会遇到很多陷阱，而在这些陷阱之中，最可怕的一种是自掘的陷阱，即贪婪。”', '155');
INSERT INTO `ms_essay` VALUES (6, 6, '孤独上瘾 ‖ 为何望着地铁上的低头族觉得恍若隔世？', '<div class=\"cover-con\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; text-align: center; color: #111111; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><img class=\"article-cover\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" title=\"孤独上瘾 ‖ 为何望着地铁上的低头族觉得恍若隔世？-心理学文章-壹心理\" src=\"https://ossimg.xinli001.com/20220224/1b4817ee3da8658e6cf4becdd2ebc3dd.jpeg?x-oss-process=image/quality,Q_80\" alt=\"孤独上瘾 ‖ 为何望着地铁上的低头族觉得恍若隔世？-心理学文章-壹心理\" /></div> <div class=\"yxl-editor\" style=\"margin: 30px 0px 0px; padding: 16px 0px 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; word-break: break-all; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"> <div class=\"yxl-editor-article \" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; min-height: 48px;\"> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">在短片《男孩丹尼》中描述的是一个拥有头颅即是异类的世界，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">只见路人们络绎不绝摩肩接踵都是没有头颅且漫无目的地走着，就算撞到了车撞到了路灯也不知道躲避的状态</span></span>，而丹尼是一个拥有头颅的异类，最后他为了&ldquo;爱&rdquo;却愿意选择平庸与迷茫，甘愿脱离自己的头颅而与心爱的人共同踏上迷茫之途。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">现实生活中很多人也是迷茫的，像是无头苍蝇一样，不知道自己存在的意义到底是什么，我们吃饭睡觉上班下班挤地铁，很多事情熟悉到似乎都已经被安排得板上钉钉般明明白白。却也不知道为什么一定要继续这样做，这样的生活似乎也没有一个头。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">有时候，会</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">望着地铁上的人群，大部分人都在刷手机，面无表情，手指在打字或者是在左划右划，非常机械</span></span>，似乎在寻找最吸引自己的短视频，瞬间中觉得自己真的是很孤单啊，就算是在人群中，也能够体会到这种寂寥的感觉。</p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">不可否认，我们是社会性的动物，离不开社交关系，离不开与人交流</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">，然而，孤独也是人类生存生活过程中的一部分，我不愿意相信孤独会被弃如敝履，没有孤独，我们怎么会产生爱与归属感的需求呢？</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">心理学家们认为孤独是一种与人际关系同样重要的基本人类需求，能够独处自洽的人也是情绪健康人格成熟的必然标志。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">我们可以想象有没有这样一种人:她们非常优秀，吃穿不愁，成绩前列，月薪过万，但是就是非常黏人，她们没有办法自己一个人吃饭，一定要有人陪着自己睡觉才能睡得着.........</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">当然这样的例子是比较极端的，不排除真实社会中的确是存在这样的人的，如果出现了这种情况，我们也需要好好思考，自己为什么会变成这样，或许许多人都曾经或者正在在孤独中挣扎。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">孤独让人认定为恐怖、无聊、可耻、孤立、不合群.......所有能够被思考到的负面词汇都可以被我们思考一个遍</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">，让我们越来越害怕成为人群中落单的那一个，当自己在一大堆人里面，比如说过年的生日聚会和吃饭聚会，其他人都有说有笑，就是自己如鲠在喉、如芒刺背、如坐针毡，这种感觉肯定不好受。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">幸运的是我们还可以通过各种努力，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">来使那些独处时间成为一种具备建设性特征的愉快的体验。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">我们可以在孤独的时候与自己内心建立联系，内心积极的孤独感可以帮助我们了解自己的内在，了解自己当下的意图和规划，而不是过多让我们的时间精力集中在其他人身上。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">无论是一个人阅读，听歌，泡脚，走进大自然，旅行，坐地铁.......我们没有必要感到无聊，没有必要感觉自己就是大海中的一叶扁舟，因为自己之外也有很多其他的船舶在航行，我<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">们可以陪伴自己，在独处的时间安然自得，在想要跳出独处的时候就寻找友情爱情亲情的滋润。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">独处之中的情绪会更加明显准确，而不带入其他的混杂，我们如果愿意进行自我反省，就可以在这样的反省中做出有效率的顿悟，内省和强迫式的反刍是不同的，洞察自己但是不强迫自己，不去做一些无意义的重复殚精竭虑，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">只要看到自己今后可以怎么做到更好即可。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">就算我们平时已经非常非常忙碌，我们的时间已经被各种沟通，各种杂事，或者是各种检测所挤兑，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">仍然从独处中获益还是非常必要的，有的人甚至独处上瘾，会从独处之中找到前所未有的快乐。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">以至于当自己以更加独立于世间的态度观看人群，观看其他人的时候，会觉得自己飘飘然羽化而登仙恍若隔世，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important;\">这种状态不能说是不好的，可能就是缺少了一丝丝烟火气吧。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">这是一项在平衡人际关系和学习工作和独处三者之时很难做到的技能。这也是非常具有挑战性的，因此我们有必要去注意一下自己在独处时候的时间是究竟如何度过的。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">好的独处必然会让人豁然开朗，会让自己的注意力更加集中，让自己的生活与内在精神更加饱满，而不好的独处只会让自己焦虑寂寞与恐惧社交或者是社恐，甚至精疲力竭。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">我们的外界存在过度的刺激，存在爆炸式的信息，很多信息都没有办法去完全吸收，所以要尽可能避免这种过度消耗状态，即使只是在周末的时候关个机，去享受一下泡温泉都是非常有意义的体验呢。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">同时为了避免自己『失联』，我们一定要知道自己何时要退出这种孤独的状态，并且主动寻求他人的陪伴，主动去发出自己的信号，重新投入到学习工作与人际关系之中。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">在判断何时退出孤独的状态时一定要注意自己是否已经对孤独上瘾，有的人可能会特别喜欢孤独的感觉，有人会因为自己没有花足够的时间独处而感到不满，甚至在经过很长时间的独处之后还会觉得『凭什么别人要侵占我的自由时间，凭什么要在我休息的时候给我信息轰炸呢？』.....这个时候个体非常容易脱离人间烟火，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">变得缺少人情味甚至去人性化淡漠，值得警惕哦！</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">其实我也相信许多喜欢独处的人这么多年来必然会思考到这一个地步，这几乎是一个必然，没有谁会有百分百的耐心对待他人的打扰和社交入侵，我们也不是神人圣人，毕竟有些人天生就会比其他人更渴望独处，这是一种主动性孤独，而不是那种社交自我存在性的被动性孤独。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">而另一方面对于那些认为自己非常孤独的人同时也是被动孤独的人来说，独处的时间越长，他们感到的抑郁就可能越多，因为他们处理孤独的能力经验还不是特别老道，她们还需要一些经验积累，让自己去在实践中慢慢了解孤独感的必要性。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">其实重要的时我们在孤独独处时间里的生活质量，在这种时间里面如果花在真正愉快和有意义的活动上，或许就可以让自己真正突破内在的桎梏，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">在疫情期间的独处是一种挑战，突如其来的封城封闭小区都容易让人产生恐惧感</span>。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">也有一些科学研究显示单身人士在隔离独处期间的幸福感要比以前减少了很多，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">这可能意味着当人们主动选择独处而不是被迫不得不独处时，那么独处无人陪伴很有可能是一种积极的体验而不是消极的体验。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">我们中的一些人被困在家里，不得不去接受独处，或者是不得不与人交流，与家里人低头不见抬头见，这些都是被动独处，被动社交，似乎主动性永远都在我们自己手上，只是这个决定的操纵杆并没有那么实体化。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">其实主动选择独处有很多好处，许多人包括我自己在大自然之中都有着最积极的独处体验，可以在森林公园漫步，在大海里漂浮，在沙滩上玩沙子，在草原上呼吸新鲜空气，看看潮起潮落，听听花鸟虫鱼的声音。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">根据孤独的人际圈层，人们被分为不同的群体，包括&ldquo;群体内&rdquo;、&ldquo;群体外&rdquo;和真正的&ldquo;孤独者&rdquo;，有一些处于群体外的人就想要去真正合群，让自己成为群里内部人群，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">其实圈子不同不必强融，有时候我们只是需要让自己享受成为孤独者的状态。</span></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">孤独者也是勇敢的人，我们可以通过努力寻找一些大自然赋予自己的敬畏，让自己不害怕孤独，同时也不会过度卷入孤独其中且不知道怎么跳脱出来，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">毕竟有时候我们也是低头族中的一员</span>，大家是不同的，也有相同之处啊。</span></p> </div> </div>', '2022-01-12 19:20:53', '2022-03-17 18:35:27', '科普', '孤独也是人类生存生活过程中的一部分，我不愿意相信孤独会被弃如敝履，没有孤独，我们怎么会产生爱与归属感的需求呢？', '432');
INSERT INTO `ms_essay` VALUES (10, 1, '逼我垃圾堆找对象，爹妈是不是有「大病」？', '<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">又到了每月一度的情人节了。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">3月14日，白色情人节，你，脱单了吗？</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">情人节前夕，为了实现34年情人节零突破，</span>我组了个相亲局。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">虽然，还是没把自己「安利<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">」</span>出去。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">但身边单身的朋友，倒是对此响应热烈。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">毕竟，如果自己不努力，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">大概率，就得沦为爹妈安排的<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">「</span>相亲大戏<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">」</span>里的男一女一。</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">91年的叶子，今年春节7天假，就被哐啷排了8场相亲。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">结果遇上的，一个比一个更像<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">「</span>奇人异士<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">」</span>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">有人见面10分钟，就说：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: inherit;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<blockquote style=\"margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border-left-width: 4px; border-left-color: #999999; font-size: 16px; color: #999999; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&ldquo;爹妈养我长大吃了很多苦，我想让他们过上好日子。&rdquo;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">嗯，很孝顺，没毛病。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: inherit;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<blockquote style=\"margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border-left-width: 4px; border-left-color: #999999; font-size: 16px; color: #999999; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&ldquo;你妈说，你家两套房，一套咱俩住，一套给我爹妈住。&rdquo;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">还没交往呢，就开始算计了。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">叶子无语了。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">她知道老妈一直觉得她长相太普通，脾气又比较火爆，只能从其他地方突破。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">可，这也太侮辱人了。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">一个没钱没品的奇葩对象，在自家父母眼里，怎么就成了<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">「</span>乘龙快婿<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">」</span>？</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">今天，壹心理就和大家聊一聊，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">父母奇葩的择媳择婿观</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">01</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">挑媳妇，不看钱只看脸，</span></span></h1>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">挑女婿，既不看钱也不看脸</span></span></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">奇葩相亲局，放之四海皆有。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">是做父母的眼光太差吗？</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">《英国心理学杂志》就曾研究过这个事。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">考虑到中国国情的特殊性，他们还专门在云南昆明做了一次田野调查。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">研究人员先找了300个父母，作为<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">「</span>父母组<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">」</span>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">云南师范大学230名大学生，以及公园里40多个<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">「</span>单身狗<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">」</span>作为<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">「</span>子女组<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">」</span>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">问卷结果显示：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">父母挑选媳妇时，主要看脸；而挑选女婿时，主要看钱。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">子女选伴侣时，大多比较看重颜值，收入排在靠后的位置。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 90%; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: block;\" src=\"https://ossimg.xinli001.com/20220314/49aaa38748275d460a25345194a90e15.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,Q_80\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">「颜值」和「收入」交叉组合后，研究人员提出了4种取舍选择。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">A、不存在取舍 高颜值+高收入VS低颜值+低收入</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">B、纠结程度低 高颜值+月收入5000元 VS 低颜值+月收入6000元</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">C、纠结程度中 高颜值+月收入3000元 VS 低颜值+月收入6000元</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">D、纠结程度高 高颜值+月收入3000元 VS 低颜值+月收入12000元</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">跟大众和心理学的认知很一致了。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">社会心理学认为，在婚姻中，伴侣的价值主要体现在3个方面：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">现实价值</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">、</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">情绪价值</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">以及</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">生理价值</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">现实价值包含金钱、权利、地位以及其他实际帮助等；</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">情绪价值指陪伴、爱情、关心、照顾等等；</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">生理价值指性、传宗接代。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">而在父母看来：</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">结婚时，伴侣「现实层面」条件的重要性，远远高于那些「虚的」。</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">从进化心理学的角度来看，这样选择也很正常。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">毕竟，从生物性的视角来看，最利于<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">「</span>传宗接代<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">」</span>的选择才是好选择。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">自古以来男主外女主内，男性提供养育价值，女性提供生育价值，彼此配合才保证种族繁衍。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">直到一百年前，在婚姻里都不配谈爱情。</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">但，令人百思不得其解的是：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">调查显示，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">还有16%的父母，在选女婿的时候。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">竟然既不看钱也不看脸，怎么磕碜怎么来！</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">明明有各方面看来都更好的选择，他们还是会选</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">「</span>财貌双低<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">」</span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">的那个。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">在网上逛了一圈，发现这类<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">「</span>奇葩<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">」</span>还不少。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">壹心理后台也有类似的留言。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 90%; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: block;\" src=\"https://ossimg.xinli001.com/20220314/fc1a9df7d52cc3c4e5a8e6cc2f29bc3f.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,Q_80\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">真让人忍不住想问：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<blockquote style=\"margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border-left-width: 4px; border-left-color: #999999; font-size: 16px; color: #999999; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">非要选那些又穷又丑的对象，这些爹妈是不是跟自家儿女有仇？</span></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">02</span></h1>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">父母并非是在故意坑女儿</span></span></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">类似的评论下，基本都是满脑袋问号：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<blockquote style=\"margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border-left-width: 4px; border-left-color: #999999; font-size: 16px; color: #999999; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">真有这么坑女儿的爸妈？</span>那男人才是你爹娘亲生的吧！</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">令人不禁怀疑，是不是爹妈中了邪。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">问题到底出在哪里？</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">表面来看，父母给出的理由，好像也挺<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">「</span>现实<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">」</span>：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<blockquote style=\"margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border-left-width: 4px; border-left-color: #999999; font-size: 16px; color: #999999; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&ldquo;有钱有权的，怕你驾驭不了他。&rdquo;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&ldquo;</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">好看有什么用，老实人才能过日子！&rdquo;</span></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">可问题是，从没有数据表明，帅的就比丑的更有花花肠子啊？</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">其实，从心理学的角度来分析，根子往往出在</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">「配得感」</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">上。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">简单来说，就是</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">「</span>觉得自己是否值得拥有<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">」</span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">无论是挑伴侣，还是做其他选择时，潜意识里，我们都在默默计算自己<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">「</span>配得到什么<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">」</span>。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&ldquo;您配吗？&rdquo;不是一句调侃，更是扎心的现实。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 90%; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: block;\" src=\"https://ossimg.xinli001.com/20220314/0c545e52a8295dbd2ef006c6dc363ae0.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,Q_80\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">在心理学看来，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">如何定义伴侣的价值，是由我们如何定义自我价值决定的</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important;\">。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">同理，父母如何选择媳妇或女婿，是由他们如何定义自我价值、以及自家儿女的价值决定的。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">事实证明，一个拥有健康配得感的人，更容易找到真正适合自己的伴侣。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">而一个拥有健康配得感的父母，择媳择婿的标准往往更客观。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">反之，一个人的配得感过高，容易高不成低不就；</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">配得感越过低，很容易低就，习惯于从垃圾堆里选人。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">同理，配得感过低的父母，会给孩子介绍「低配」伴侣。</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">朋友子墨，不久前相了一个她妈口中的「高质量男性」。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<blockquote style=\"margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border-left-width: 4px; border-left-color: #999999; font-size: 16px; color: #999999; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">她妈说：</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&ldquo;</span>他挺不错的，很孝顺，工作稳定，不抽烟不喝酒，脾气好。&rdquo;&nbsp;</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">因为圈子里的男人大多挣得还行，但太飘了，她由衷觉得找个踏实的也不错。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">可聊了不到 3 句话就emo了。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">无论她说什么，男人都要扯到「女孩子还是赶紧回家考个公务员吧」。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">不想结婚后连最基本的交流都没有，子墨当即表示</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">「我们不适合」。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">没曾想，一回到家就被老妈炮轰：</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: inherit;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<blockquote style=\"margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border-left-width: 4px; border-left-color: #999999; font-size: 16px; color: #999999; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&ldquo;你左挑右挑，以为自己是仙女吗？&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&ldquo;</span>你也不看看自己多大了，差不多就行了。&rdquo;</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: inherit;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">在她看来，有个性别为男的人搭伙过日子就该心满意足了。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">再多的要求，都是矫情。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<blockquote style=\"margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border-left-width: 4px; border-left-color: #999999; font-size: 16px; color: #999999; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&ldquo;我跟你爸不都是这么过来的吗？&rdquo;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">可她过得并不幸福，经常跟子墨抱怨。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">即便如此，依然不自觉地将女儿推向同样的男人。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">多年来，妈妈潜意识里的不配得感，让她觉得低就是唯一的选择。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">同时，也将这样的标准强加到孩子身上。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">精神分析称之为</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">「</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">投射」</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">她无法看到女儿真正的价值和真实的需求，脑子里满是对自己和孩子的差评，和扭曲的认知形象。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">这样的心态，往往会导致挑选结婚对象时，特别草率。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">仿佛有什么难言之隐，只盼着有人接盘似的。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">而那个「占了大便宜」的结婚对象，往往也不会感激你的「低就」「扶贫」，软饭硬吃才是理所当然。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 90%; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: block;\" src=\"https://ossimg.xinli001.com/20220314/292ec672657f6668c07b54cb47a71fdb.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,Q_80\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">03</span></h1>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">家里有皇位等着继承的，</span></span></h1>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">又是怎么回事？</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">还有一类父母则相反，他们的配得感过高，尤其是挑媳妇的时候。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">朋友小艺，最近跟男友回家见了家长。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">她在某国企做总助，收入体面；</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">父母早早给配了房、车；</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">小艺本人更是漂亮乖巧，气质出众。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">按世俗的标准，无论是长相、能力、性格、家世，配小县城工人家庭的男友，都绰绰有余。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">他也很清楚，当初在校园里，是他苦苦追的小艺。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">然而，见了男友父母后，却忍不住怀疑他是不是拿了什么隐形大鳄的剧本。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">他们历数着追他儿子的人多么优秀，但都被拒了。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">字字句句，都是</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">「能跟他们儿子在一起是莫大的恩宠」</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">小艺傻了。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 90%; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: block;\" src=\"https://ossimg.xinli001.com/20220314/123f0658c61db892cdc382eb96e3e8ac.png?x-oss-process=image/quality,Q_80\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">配得感过高的父母，特别自恋，都是透过光圈看自家孩子，却用哈哈镜看别人</span>。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">在他们潜意识里，往往觉得任何人都配不上自家孩子。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">因此，哪怕又美又能干、开药店养活老公、为男人偷仙草漫金山的白素贞。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">她都会挑剔：</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">你是个妖怪，我家纳你进门，是抬举你！</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">这类人有一个统称，叫「全能自恋者」。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">指的是：自认为我是无所不能的，整个世界都应该按照我的意愿来运转。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">PUA大师一般就是他们。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">看起来，配得感过高和配得感过低是截然不同的人。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">其实，他们内在，都有两个割裂的我。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">一个「我」，丑陋，平庸，弱小，无能，愚蠢&hellip;&hellip;</span>配不上世间一切美好的存在，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">是阴影里见不得光的鬼；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">另一个「我」，完美，独特，强大，全能，聪慧&hellip;&hellip;</span>不可能有人不喜欢和崇拜我，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">是全知全能的神。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">唯独没有一个真实的、普通的、有好也有坏、有能也有不能的</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">「人」</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">于是，配得感过低的人，把「全不能」的我，留给了自己；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">而配得感过高的人，把「全不能」投射给了别人。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">事实上，本质是一样的，都是因为不敢面对真实的自我。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">于是，只能活在常人看来，「不可理喻」的世界。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">04</span></h1>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">结语</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">回到最初的问题，父母的择偶标准怎么如此奇葩？</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">到这里，我们已经有了答案</span>。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 90%; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: block;\" src=\"https://ossimg.xinli001.com/20220314/870901b78ec3c80a461cc72eecf6fbf3.jpeg?x-oss-process=image/quality,Q_80\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">父母之所以会有如此怪异的脑回路。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">大多数时候，并不是因为不够爱你，或者刻意作践你。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">更可能的原因，是他们对伴侣的定义过于狭隘，或者「配得感」失衡。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">当然，这口锅，也不能完完全全扣在父母头上。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">他们的态度，多多少少与儿女不经意的表态有关，更与儿女自己展现出来的价值感有关。</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">比如，同处小镇，同为「剩女」。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">爸妈从来不给我介绍对象，因为他们知道我很「挑」。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">但是，我妹却被安排了不下50次相亲。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">方圆百里各路奇葩，全被搜罗了来。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">所以，若真的受不了父母的安排，一定要沟通、沟通、再沟通。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">毕竟，自己婚姻都没整明白的父母，其实也搞不清楚你适合什么样的人。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">当然。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">为了「人类和平」，最好不要说「你怎么老给我介绍这样的人？」</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<blockquote style=\"margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border-left-width: 4px; border-left-color: #999999; font-size: 16px; color: #999999; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">试着换成：</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&ldquo;我觉得找对象也要有目标才行，不能这么继续瞎碰运气，太浪费时间，你孩子也老大不小了。&rdquo;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">第一步表达认同、统一立场，表明自己也在为「终身大事」上心。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">然后，把父母的标准梳理出来。</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: inherit;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<blockquote style=\"margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border-left-width: 4px; border-left-color: #999999; font-size: 16px; color: #999999; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&ldquo;</span>你们给我介绍的这几个对象，好像&hellip;&hellip;&rdquo;&nbsp;</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">最后，说清楚自己的标准和态度。</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote style=\"margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border-left-width: 4px; border-left-color: #999999; font-size: 16px; color: #999999; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&ldquo;我想要共度一生的人，一定要123，绝对不能456&hellip;&hellip;&rdquo;&nbsp;</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">如果父母就是固执己见，打心眼里觉得&ldquo;你懂什么，我们又不可能害你&rdquo;呢？&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">最有力的回应不是说「别管我」，而是让他们看到：不需要父母介绍，我也能凭实力脱单。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">若压根不想进入婚姻？</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">就更要让他们看到即便是独自一人，我依然可以过得很滋润。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">最最最重要的是：</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">不管结婚与否，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">都要坚定地给自己很多很多爱，做自己的「理想伴侣」。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">毕竟，人生在世，倏尔百年。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">不是为了结婚。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">而是为了幸福。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">世界和我爱着你。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">配得感测试：</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">以下一些问题，可以帮你测一测自己的配得感有多高。（也可以给父母测测呀）</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">1、别人对你好时，会觉得一定是别有所图吗？</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">2、偶然得到一件比较贵重的礼物，会舍不得用吗？</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">3、是否总是怕麻烦别人？</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">4、是否习惯于把好的东西都留给家人，不舍得在自己身上花钱？</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">5、看到比较优秀的异性，是否觉得ta一定不会喜欢我？</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">6、是否觉得不该对另一半提要求？7、是否觉得只有找比自己差的人，才可能幸福？</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">8、是否习惯于迁就对方？9、是否过于在乎对方的感受，而习惯性忽视自己的需求？</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">10、是否花大量时间、精力去找打折商品、忍耐各种不合理？&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">A、总是&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;B、常常&nbsp;&nbsp;C、偶尔&nbsp;&nbsp;D、从不&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">A选项越多，配得感越低；</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">D选项越多，配得感越高。&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">你的结果是什么呢？&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">若你的得分太低了，不妨问一问自己：</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&ldquo;哪里不配呢？&rdquo;&ldquo;这是真的吗？&rdquo;&ldquo;有没有和我差不多却配上的人呢？&rdquo;&ldquo;如何让自己更配得上呢？&rdquo;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">愿大家永远都用不上&ldquo;你配吗？&rdquo;表情包。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>', '2022-03-18 10:49:01', '2022-03-18 10:49:01', '关于自我', '无论是挑伴侣，还是做其他选择时，潜意识里，我们都在默默计算自己「配得到什么」', NULL);
INSERT INTO `ms_essay` VALUES (9, 1, '儿童青少年心理健康成两会热点话题', '<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">两会已经开始了，不知道你有没有关注？</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">如果你有关注的话，不难发现，今年的两会上，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">儿童青少年心理健康问题，又是一个热点议题！</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">近年来，随着社会发展、竞争压力和亲子关系的变化，青少年精神疾病特别是情绪障碍呈上升趋势。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">每年的全国两会上，都能看到全国人大代表、全国政协委员关心青少年心理健康的相关议案、提案和建议。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">前不久，喜猫才介绍过<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #0066cc; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.xinli001.com/info/100481986\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"nofollow\">洛阳理工学院副院长、全国政协委员马珺建议将学生群体心理治疗纳入医保</a></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">（点击蓝字查看原文）</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">的信息。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">这一两天内，又有<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">包括前新东方教育集团董事长俞敏洪在内的多个政协委员，针对青少年的心理健康问题，提交了提案。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">01</span></h1>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">俞敏洪</span></h1>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">重视青少年抑郁预防和治疗</span></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">俞敏洪今年向大会提交了</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">《关于重视青少年抑郁预防和治疗的建议》</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">的提案，指出&mdash;&mdash;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">《中国国民心理健康发展报告（2019－2020）》显示：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote class=\"\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border-left-width: 4px; border-left-color: #999999; font-size: 16px; color: #999999; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-type=\"2\" data-url=\"\" data-author-name=\"\" data-content-utf8-length=\"134\" data-source-title=\"\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">2020年青少年抑郁检出率为24.6%。其中轻度抑郁17.2%，重度抑郁为7.4%；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">小学阶段抑郁检出率为1成，其中重度抑郁为1.9-3.3%；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">初中阶段抑郁检出率约为3成，其中重度抑郁为7.6%-8.6%；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">高中阶段抑郁检出率近4成，其中重度抑郁为10.9%-12.5%。</span></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">2018年北医儿童发展中心《中国儿童自杀报告》显示:&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote class=\"\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border-left-width: 4px; border-left-color: #999999; font-size: 16px; color: #999999; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-type=\"2\" data-url=\"\" data-author-name=\"\" data-content-utf8-length=\"65\" data-source-title=\"\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">中国每年约有10万青少年死于自杀；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">每分钟就有2位青少年死于自杀，还有8位自杀未遂；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">绝大部分青少年自杀案例都与抑郁症状或抑郁症有关。</span></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">根据民间抗郁组织渡过平台内部的观察数据，青少年抑郁高发的成因可以归结为以下四点：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">一、学业竞争，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">除了学习时长、课程难度、考试等因素，更大的问题是攀比；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">二、人际关系</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">，包括家庭关系、家校关系、师生关系、同伴关系等；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">三、成长问题</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">，很多社会现象会给单纯的孩子们带来巨大冲击；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">四、生活方式</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">，比如沉迷网络、作息紊乱、网购频繁、缺乏运动等。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">针对上述现象，俞敏洪在提案提出了四条建议。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">1.建立教育部等部门联合行动的机制，形成<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">全社会重视青少年精神困惑问题</span>的氛围；落实《教育部办公厅关于加强学生心理健康管理工作的通知》，加强青少年学生心理健康管理的<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">专业支撑和科学方法</span>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">2.<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">减轻课业负担</span>，开展丰富课外活动，锻炼组织能力、领导能力、交流能力、团队协作能力、执行力；让孩子们有更多的机会亲近自然，在自然的环境下学习体验。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">3.鼓励公益慈善组织牵头<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">构建精神疾病疗愈社会支持系统</span>，以弥补现有医疗系统和心理咨询系统的不足。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">4.<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">提升学校心理老师的心理专业知识水平和心理督导、咨询能力</span>，提升班主任老师、教职员工对学生精神心理问题的识别能力，以及应用心理学知识处理学生心理问题的能力。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">02</span></h1>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">刘庆峰</span></h1>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">加大青少年抑郁症筛查</span></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">同样关注儿童青少年抑郁预防和治疗的还有全国人大代表、科大讯飞股份有限公司董事长刘庆峰。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">在本次两会中，刘庆峰表示：&ldquo;目前我国抑郁症呈低龄化趋势，要警惕把青少年抑郁症当做青春叛逆来对待。&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">在提案中，刘庆峰同样提到<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">要&ldquo;重视心理教育，加强建设学校心理健康必修课程及讲座&rdquo;，并且要求学校&ldquo;配足心理辅导老师&rdquo;。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">而且和马珺一样，刘庆峰也建议：<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">将抑郁症及心理咨询纳入医保，并且归类为&ldquo;慢性病病种&rdquo;。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">这样做的好处有两个：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">1.减少患者病耻感和歧视，降低患者经济负担；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">2.加强规范化治疗，惠及更多中轻度患者。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">同时，刘庆峰还建议，要设立&ldquo;专题攻关项目&rdquo;：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">加速推进人工智能技术在心理疾病及抑郁症管理中的应用，建立心理健康服务平台和抑郁症智能筛查平台，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">为全国中小学进行全量筛查</span>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">03</span></h1>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">施卫东<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /></span></h1>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">加强学生抑郁症筛查隐私保护</span></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">同样关注儿童青少年抑郁筛查的，还有南通大学校长施卫东。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">如果你还记得，自从去年九月教育部发文决定将抑郁筛查纳入中小学体检之后，就引起了很大的热议。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">一方面是对这个政策的赞许，尤其是心理从业者和为学生心理健康担忧的家长；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">但另一方面，也有很多心理人提出了担忧，包括<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">如何保证测量足够专业、如何在筛查后不造成抑郁学生更大的压力，以及如何保障学生的隐私。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">几年两会，南通大学校长施卫东就提出：抑郁症筛查体检应<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">加强对未成年人的隐私保密</span>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">对此，他提出了三条建议：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">1.考虑以学年为单位，未成年学生及家长可自主选择筛查时间和医院，医院对结果异常者进行&ldquo;点对点&rdquo;告知，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">学校获知筛查结果应严格限定人员知晓范围</span>；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">2.教育部门应出台抑郁症筛查学生体检明细规程，制定学生心理健康隐私保护办法及<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">隐私泄露追责机制</span>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">3.学生抑郁症筛查应<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">采用多次筛查</span>，不搞&ldquo;一检定性&rdquo;，提高筛查的准确性。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">当然，保护儿童青少年的心理健康，不能只靠量表筛查。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">家庭、学校、社会三方面共同发力，从预防、干预到治疗三者都抓起来，才能全面保障学生的心理健康。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">本次大会上，有三份提案分别对这三方面提出了建议。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">04</span></h1>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">马瑞燕</span></h1>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">所有育龄家长普及心理健康知识</span></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">第一份提案是全国人大代表、山西农业大学植物保护学院院长马瑞燕提出来的，关于加强青少年儿童心理健康问题家庭预防的建议。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">马瑞燕表示：&ldquo;通过对国内19所涉农高校32个学院（二级教学单位）进行调研（微信、电话），<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">发现80%以上中、重度大学生心理问题根源都在原生家庭。</span>&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">如何才能预防原生家庭给儿童青少年造成心理伤害？</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">马瑞燕建议：<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">向所有育龄家长普及心理健康知识。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">包括：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote class=\"\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border-left-width: 4px; border-left-color: #999999; font-size: 16px; color: #999999; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-type=\"2\" data-url=\"\" data-author-name=\"\" data-content-utf8-length=\"184\" data-source-title=\"\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">1.为所有育龄家长开设家长课堂，普及抑郁症、不同年龄段儿童成长规律和心理特征相关知识；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">2.编撰出版少年儿童心理学科普类书籍，制作少年儿童典型心理问题表现及家长正确应对的科普读本和视频资料，提高家长对孩子心理健康问题的关注度和识别能力；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">3.借助主流媒体以各种形式正向宣传普及心理、精神疾病等相关知识，设计制作播演比较典型、有影响的亲子交流互动教育节目，构建和谐家庭氛围。</span></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">同时，马瑞燕也建议要&ldquo;加强学科专项研究和筛查力度&rdquo;以及&ldquo;加大青少年儿童精神卫生服务体系建设和投入&rdquo;。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">05</span></h1>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">柴会恩</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\" /></span></h1>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">加强中小学心理教育师资</span></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">第二份提案则是全国人大代表、河北定州市西关南街小学副校长柴会恩的建议：<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">加强对学校心理健康教育的政策支持，制定和完善支持与鼓励的相关政策措施。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">其中最主要的，就是加强中小学心理教育师资。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">包括：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">1.提升学校心理教师待遇</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">在工作条件、岗位编制、职称待遇、经费设置、科研进修等方面对心理教育教师给于相应的政策支持与鼓励措施，使得优秀人才或在职教师从事中小学心理健康教育工作。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">2.加强学校心理教师的培训与督导</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">成立中小学心理健康教育专家指导机构，择优遴选有未成年人心理健康辅导工作经历的教师，在教育行政部门领导下，开展中小学心理健康教育教学的研究、研判、咨询、指导、评估、服务等工作。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">而如果大家还记得，之前喜猫也发过多次文章，反映学校心理教师的执业困境，其中最主要的两个点，就是待遇偏低和缺乏专业培训。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">本次柴会恩的建议，则针对这两个问题提出了建议。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">当然，我们不能指望它一次性解决所有问题，但至少，是一个良好的开端。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">06</span></h1>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">邱光和</span></h1>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">二级以上医院开设青少年心理健康专科</span></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">除了学校需要人才的培养和引进，社会医疗体系中的人才和各种资源，也需要得到加强。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">全国人大代表、森马集团有限公司董事长邱光和就表示：&ldquo;解决心理健康问题有三个关键环节：预防、预警、干预。目前，对已有心理问题的孩子，在干预环节，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">公共医疗供给严重不足。</span>&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">喜猫之前也提到过，精神专科人才队伍的缺乏是导致各类心理、精神疾病确诊和治疗不足的因素之一。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">据了解，目前精神心理专科在各大三甲综合性医院的配备力量不足，平均仅有2～3人。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">而针对儿童青少年的心理健康专科则更是寥寥无几。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">邱光和提到，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">大部分医院还没有专门的儿童青少年心理健康专科</span>，二级以上精神专科医院设立儿童青少年心理门诊的不到60%，儿童专科医院、妇幼保健院、二级以上综合医院开设精神（心理）门诊的不到30%。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">此外，专业人才也严重缺乏。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">对此邱光和提出了两个建议：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">1.由国家卫健委疾控局出台指导意见，鼓励<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">二级以上医院开设青少年心理健康专科</span>，配备精神专业医师；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\">2.加大专业儿童精神科医生的培养力度，力争<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">各省每10万人平均有2至3名专门服务未成年人的精神科医生</span>。</span></p>', '2022-03-18 10:31:46', '2022-03-18 10:42:09', '科普', '2020年青少年抑郁检出率为24.6%。其中轻度抑郁17.2%，重度抑郁为7.4%；', NULL);
INSERT INTO `ms_essay` VALUES (11, 4, '“没啥好回送的，我送你走吧”', '<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">我不允许还有人没加入&ldquo;劝分组&rdquo;。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">要说收看当今都市爱情故事大戏，一定不是八点档的电视剧，也不是早就过时的言情杂志，而是实时更新、涌动着真实丰富又离谱荒唐故事的&ldquo;劝分组&rdquo;。逢年过节更是好戏连台。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">在刚过去的情人节，劝分组又让大家见识了不少抠门男频大戏。比如屏幕点燃迪士尼烟花，大方送我166g蚂蚁森林能量，把钱借给别人过情人节了，以及0.52的红包&hellip;&hellip;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">一方面让人大呼又见世面了，一方面也让人心生疑窦：从什么时候开始，物质交易成为了浪漫爱情的主流表达形式？</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><img style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 90%; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; border: 0px; vertical-align: top; display: block;\" src=\"https://ossimg.xinli001.com/20220313/18233c2d800eb61620df5119f7339655.jpeg?x-oss-process=image/quality,Q_80\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">01</span></h1>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">基于消费主义的爱情</span></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">如今，各种各样的商业化交易形式已经成为了践行浪漫传统的先决条件。例如，如果你想要开始一段恋爱，或者维持已有的恋爱关系，你都不可避免地要与恋爱对象面对面或通过网络视频交流，因此，一副符合大众审美的皮囊必不可少。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">世人皆有爱美之心，虽然大众对美貌的追求已是司空见惯，但&ldquo;女为悦己者容&rdquo;这一重复行为预示着新的美容技巧层出不穷，甚至超越了个人的审美范畴。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">对美的渴求已经等同于追求美丽的视觉享受。外表美丽并不是衡量美的唯一标准，但却成为了人们趋之若鹜的唯一目标。每个人对美都有着不同的理解，一些女性会去美容，例如去化妆和脱毛。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">一旦有了伴侣，对美的理解与追求就又增加了一个维度，你会想要猜测伴侣心目中的理想型。由此带来的心理负担成倍增加：除了要考虑自己的审美眼光之外，还要注重考虑伴侣的审美标准和喜好。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">由对美的追求而衍生出层出不穷的美容产品和服务，无疑提高了公司的绩效，却并没有促进我们恋爱关系的发展。当我们购买商品装扮自己，去追求时刻变化的主流审美，这些公司赚得盆满钵满。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">恋爱中缺乏安全感，导致我们无休止地进行消费，一些跨国公司成了获利者。数字媒体下的大众主流审美不断更新变化，影响着我们的审美标准与对美的追求，于是我们继续保持着对外表的投资。有时人们并不认可这种审美标准，但还是在商业公司的鼓吹和宣传之下，接受了这种形象。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">02</span></h1>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">爱情＝物质交易？</span></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">有时，即使生理上的情感也需要借由物质上的交易表达出来。例如，当我们收到伴侣的礼物或惊喜时，我们最常见的反应就是给他们一个拥抱或是亲吻，由此加深情感。这种亲密的举动成为了我们对接受物质赠予时表达感激之情的方式，这些物质可能是一块手表，几张水上乐园的门票。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">在收到伴侣送给我们的礼物后，我们会用爱来回报他们。<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">每一次的交易所带来的感恩和回报都是一次正强化，鼓励伴侣在经济上和情感上继续投入，交换的过程永远不会结束。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">社交平台上自称是爱情导师的那些人经常重申情侣之间保持&ldquo;新鲜感&rdquo;的重要性，鼓励人们不断创造新的体验，带给彼此惊喜。在当下以数字为媒介的经济社会中，恋爱中交换礼物十分常见。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">虽然爱情并不一定要建立在礼物交换的基础之上，但不可否认的是，礼物和惊喜的确创造了很多浪漫时刻。这在某种程度上也表明了，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">除了经济上的付出带来的浪漫惊喜，我们越来越无法理解其他形式的浪漫了</span>。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">但要注意的是，这类浪漫交易并不适用于所有人。许多人负担不起现代城市中物物交换的浪漫惊喜，这一点也是很多情感博主和恋爱导师们都忽视的地方，要求伴侣为你付出并非不合情理，但许多人没有足够的经济实力去践行所谓的情感博主和爱情广告中宣扬的浪漫传统。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">一旦我们认可了&ldquo;他不为你花钱就是不爱你&rdquo;，我们就会要求伴侣的经济条件，他们要有足够的经济实力才能成为我们的&ldquo;灵魂伴侣&rdquo;。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">一旦接受了这一价值观，这种&ldquo;浪漫&rdquo;循环就会持续下去。人们花大价钱盛装打扮并与伴侣见面。他们买礼物送给伴侣。他们从伴侣那里得到情感回馈。<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">在&ldquo;商业化爱情&rdquo;的背后，他们之所以认定了对方就是自己想要与之共度余生的人，究其根本，就在于他们相信这就是&ldquo;灵魂伴侣&rdquo;该有的样子。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">我们将爱情建立在这种不稳定的物质交易之上，随着一次次交易，我们越来越疲惫，情感负担不断加重。任何一对相爱的夫妻都不想最后以分开告终，但有时候却不得已作出这个决定。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">例如，我的一个朋友自2019年以来就一直在考虑分手。但三年后，她仍然与在2018年时交往的伴侣在一起。她刚刚21岁，但她担心，如果结束这段令她不太满意的感情，她可能再也遇不到更合适的人选了。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">03</span></h1>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.5; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">&ldquo;灵魂伴侣&rdquo;的标准并不唯一</span></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">我们亲身的感情经历，在日常生活中听到的其他人的感情经历，以及社会上种种对于伴侣关系的预期，都导致了我们在感情中迟疑不决。重要的是，我们要反复思考这些所谓的爱情箴言是不是真的对我们有用，真的符合自身的情况。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">千禧一代和后千禧一代相信网上流传的&ldquo;灵魂伴侣&rdquo;之说，但这也有可能会让我们很难摆脱那些给我们情感上或身体上带来痛苦的关系。<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">一味相信&ldquo;灵魂伴侣&rdquo;，可能会令我们局限于那个&ldquo;真命天子/天女&rdquo;，让我们局限于一段不值得继续下去的恋爱关系，甚至婚姻。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; color: #444444; font-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">对我们许多人来说，浪漫的感情可能是一种深刻的人类需求，但它可以以各种方式存在。<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1; font-weight: 700 !important; font-size: inherit !important;\">浪漫的爱情不仅仅是物质上的交易，更是情感上的依恋，亲密与支持</span>。如果一段关系开始让我们喘不过气，那么与伴侣分离也未尝不可，这并不是对爱情的亵渎和污名化。</p>', '2022-03-18 11:32:38', '2022-03-18 11:32:38', '关于自我', '情人节送五毛二的红包？“没啥好回送的，我送你走吧”', NULL);
